  m_text: " The Dewdropper is a lethargic being that has the intelligence of a three
    year old. Upon seeing a creature non-slime-like, it\u2019ll pull all of its focus
    on attacking it to the best of its ability. Due to its slowness, it spits out
    a slime-like ball that hurts anyone nearby but otherwise, it is quite easy to
    out-maneuver the creature."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
