  m_text: "The Eye of Raw is a massive eye with sparkles around it, showing off its\u2026
    beauty. The Eye of Raw makes its way through the dungeon looking for players
    with whom it can overwhelm its fabulousness with. It hovers near the roof of
    the dungeon, and when a person comes into sight-range, the creature shoots a
    beam from its eyes. It may take a while to charge up. It\u2019s best to hide
    behind pillars to avoid its attack."
